item.description:
Last Minute Golf Meet up for anyone who can make it. This course requires a credit card guarantee so I will have to confirm with them no later than 7/3 at 5pm due to the Holiday. Any late comers, I will try to call after the 3rd.

The Twilight Rate is $30 after 4pm and $16 for cart if needed. The first T time is 4:03 pm.
I will be at the practice facility prior to 3:30pm and outside the pro shop around 3:40pm.

If anyone has any questions, concerns, suggestions, etc. please don't hesitate to send an email or call.

Cindi

339-224-1377
cduclos@sandco.com
